etails provided at the end of this Privacy Policy.\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><strong>How we collect Anonymous Information</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe automatically collect general website traffic information and statistics (such as your IP address for the purpose of system administration, in order to assess how many people have visited the website, most popular pages visited etc). We also collect other information which alone may not be used to identify you, such as demographic and health information. This information is collected into aggregate results in order to evaluate our service and business practice in an effort to provide you with an optimum shopping experience.\r\n\r\nWe may share non-personal, aggregated information with our partners for research purposes and may disclose how many customers bought a specific product or used a specific service such as an email list.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li><strong> How we Collect Your Personal Information</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe collect personal information submitted by you on a voluntary basis to manage and deliver your order, to keep you informed of Kate Morgan Weight loss products and services and to provide you with support while you are on the Weigh tloss program. This personal information may be voluntarily submitted by you when you fill in an order form for products or services, become a member, subscribe to our newsletter, submit a post in our forum or provide us with feedback.\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li><strong> How we Use and Disclosure Your Personal Information</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe will use the personal information as supplied by you to enable us to process and deliver your order for products and services, to provide marketing information on our products and services and specials from time to time which we believe may be of interest to you. You may advise us at any time should you wish to be removed from any or all of our marketing communications.\r\n\r\nWe may disclose certain personal info