te easier to use and may assist the user by saving time, e.g. the user will not be required to continually enter their password or ‘sign in’ again upon return visits to the website. Cookies allow our servers to keep track of customer details between visits to our website.\r\n\r\nThe information stored by the cookie includes the data that is provided during online registration. This information is only accessible online when a customer enters their username and password. Other information stored by a cookie includes website traffic data. This is not used to identify individual details but only collated into aggregate anonymous results in order to evaluate and improve our shopping service for our customers.\r\n\r\nCredit Card Information is never stored in the cookie.\r\n\r\nYou do not have to accept cookies in order to use our website and you may adjust your web browser in order to be notified when you receive a cookie or to reject cookies, however if you choose to reject cookies there may be some loss of functionality of our website and convenience of product and other offerings to you.\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n	<li><strong> Email Addresses</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe will store your email address if you send us a query, place an order or subscribe to an email list. Your email address is used for the purpose you provide it for and statistical information only, and is never disclosed to any third parties for any other purpose without your consent.\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\n	<li><strong> Spam</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe will never knowingly send you electronic messages without your consent, however we may send you information about the products and services that we offer, opportunities that may be of benefit to you and the like. You may inform us at any time if you do not wish to receive any such information from us.\r\n<ol start=\"9\">\r\n	<li><strong> Data Security</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe will take all reasonable steps to preserve the privacy of your personal info